Class DefaultTaskSystemFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.streamline.engine.impl.DefaultTaskSystemFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.daisy.streamline.api.tasks.TaskSystemFactory
    public class DefaultTaskSystemFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.daisy.streamline.api.tasks.TaskSystemFactory
    Provides a default task system factory. The default task system collects possible steps from the task group factory and finds a path through the exisiting task groups, if possible.
